data.description: Accepted Offer with Contingencies. Beautifully updated 3 bedroom, 2 bath, 1,186 sq. ft. home is located in desirable SE Albany neighborhood, across from Periwinkle school. Features spacious living room with Pellet Stove insert, skylights, sunroom, and nicely landscaped yard with new shed. Many updates include vinyl windows, roof, gutters, wiring throughout, furnace, heat pump with Central AC, hot water heater, countertops in kitchen and enlarged windows. This home will not last long!
